Class AnnotationDeclaration

  • java.lang.Object
    • cetus.hir.Declaration
      • cetus.hir.AnnotationDeclaration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Annotatable, Printable, Traversable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class AnnotationDeclaration
extends Declaration
    AnnotationDeclaration is used for stand-alone annotations in non-executable code section, e.g., in a TranslationUnit.
